# Homebrew users 

Current set up allows specific users to run linuxbrew on their home directory. 

# Install and updates of packages 
Due to the shared nature of linuxbrew setup install of new packages will be done upon request and using a single user linuxbrew user. 
This is to prevent permission on ownership of packages via brew 

# List packages 
 To list installed packeges 

 `brew list `

 # Requesting packages 
 To request packages create/raise an issue with the packege name and version